PrecisAmendment to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS by which assistance provided to a taxpayer under Part 1 or 2 of the Employee Investment Act (British Columbia) in respect of a share in the capital stock of a corporation will not be included in a taxpayer's income or reduce the cost to the taxpayer of the share.
